VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=paste_your_key_here
VITE_WEATHER_KEY=paste_your_key_here

**Get the keys:**
- Google Maps → console.cloud.google.com → New project → Enable "Maps JavaScript API" + "Directions API" + "Places API" → Credentials → Create API Key
- OpenWeatherMap → openweathermap.org → Sign up free → API keys tab → copy key